	<item>
		<title>Long Stays</title>
		<link>https://meridian.vagra.ai/long-stays/</link>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Extended Stay Program</h2>
<p>For stays of 14 nights or more, The Meridian offers a dedicated long-stay program with preferential rates, weekly housekeeping customization, and access to our resident lounge on the 18th floor.</p>
<h3>What's included</h3>
<ul>
<li>15% discount on published room rates</li>
<li>Complimentary laundry service (weekly)</li>
<li>Access to the resident lounge and pantry kitchen</li>
<li>Dedicated point of contact on the front desk</li>
<li>Flexible housekeeping schedule</li>
</ul>
<p>Contact our reservations team to discuss availability and rates for your dates.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>page</wp:post_type>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
		<wp:post_name>long-stays</wp:post_name>
		<wp:menu_order>4</wp:menu_order>
	</item>

	<item>
		<title>Offers</title>
		<link>https://meridian.vagra.ai/offers/</link>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Current Offers</h2>
<h3>Weekend Escape</h3>
<p>Book a Friday and Saturday night and receive Sunday complimentary. Includes breakfast for two at The Grill Room. Available through September 2026.</p>
<h3>Early Bird Rate</h3>
<p>Reserve 30 days in advance and save 20% on any room category. Non-refundable, but the savings are substantial.</p>
<h3>Suite Upgrade</h3>
<p>Book any Deluxe room for three or more nights and receive a complimentary upgrade to a Suite, subject to availability at check-in.</p>
<p>All offers are subject to availability. Contact reservations or use our online booking system.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>page</wp:post_type>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
		<wp:post_name>offers</wp:post_name>
		<wp:menu_order>5</wp:menu_order>
	</item>

	<item>
		<title>Gift Cards</title>
		<link>https://meridian.vagra.ai/gift-cards/</link>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Meridian Gift Cards</h2>
<p>Give the gift of a stay at The Meridian. Our gift cards are available in any denomination from $100 to $5,000 and can be applied to room reservations, dining, spa treatments, or any hotel service.</p>
<h3>How it works</h3>
<ul>
<li>Choose your amount</li>
<li>Add a personal message</li>
<li>Receive a beautifully designed digital card or a physical card mailed to you</li>
<li>Cards never expire</li>
</ul>
<p>To purchase, please contact our front desk at +1 (212) 555-0199 or email stay@themeridian.example.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>page</wp:post_type>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
		<wp:post_name>gift-cards</wp:post_name>
		<wp:menu_order>6</wp:menu_order>
	</item>

	<item>
		<title>Careers</title>
		<link>https://meridian.vagra.ai/careers/</link>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Work at The Meridian</h2>
<p>We are a team of 220 people who believe that hospitality is a craft, not a script. Most of our staff have been with us for more than five years. We promote from within and invest in training.</p>
<h3>Current Openings</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Front Desk Associate</strong> — Full-time, rotating shifts</li>
<li><strong>Housekeeping Supervisor</strong> — Full-time, mornings</li>
<li><strong>Line Cook, The Grill Room</strong> — Full-time, evenings</li>
<li><strong>Spa Therapist</strong> — Part-time, flexible hours</li>
</ul>
<p>To apply, send your CV and a short note about why you are interested to careers@themeridian.example.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>page</wp:post_type>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
		<wp:post_name>careers</wp:post_name>
		<wp:menu_order>7</wp:menu_order>
	</item>

	<item>
		<title>Privacy Policy</title>
		<link>https://meridian.vagra.ai/privacy/</link>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>The Meridian Hotel ("we", "us", "our") respects the privacy of our guests and website visitors. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect personal information.</p>
<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>When you make a reservation or inquiry, we collect your name, email, phone number, and payment details. We also collect browsing data through cookies to improve our website experience.</p>
<h3>How We Use Your Data</h3>
<p>We use your data to process reservations, communicate about your stay, and improve our services. We do not sell personal data to third parties.</p>
<h3>Contact</h3>
<p>For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at privacy@themeridian.example.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>page</wp:post_type>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
		<wp:post_name>privacy</wp:post_name>
		<wp:menu_order>10</wp:menu_order>
	</item>

	<item>
		<title>Terms &amp; Conditions</title>
		<link>https://meridian.vagra.ai/terms/</link>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>
<h3>Reservations</h3>
<p>All reservations are subject to availability. A valid credit card is required at the time of booking. Cancellations must be made at least 48 hours before the check-in date to avoid charges.</p>
<h3>Check-in / Check-out</h3>
<p>Check-in time is 3:00 PM. Check-out time is 11:00 AM. Early check-in and late check-out may be arranged subject to availability.</p>
<h3>Resort Fee</h3>
<p>A daily resort fee of $35 applies to all reservations. This includes Wi-Fi, fitness center access, and local phone calls.</p>
<h3>Liability</h3>
<p>The hotel is not responsible for loss or damage to personal belongings. A safe is provided in each room for valuables.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>page</wp:post_type>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
		<wp:post_name>terms</wp:post_name>
		<wp:menu_order>11</wp:menu_order>
	</item>

	<item>
		<title>Accessibility</title>
		<link>https://meridian.vagra.ai/accessibility/</link>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>The Meridian is committed to providing an accessible experience for all guests.</p>
<h3>Property Features</h3>
<ul>
<li>Wheelchair-accessible entrance and lobby</li>
<li>Elevators to all floors with braille signage</li>
<li>Accessible rooms with roll-in showers, grab bars, and lowered fixtures</li>
<li>Hearing-accessible rooms with visual alerts and TTY phones</li>
<li>Service animals welcome throughout the property</li>
</ul>
<h3>Website Accessibility</h3>
<p>We aim to conform to WCAG 2.1 Level AA standards. If you encounter any accessibility barriers on our website, please contact us at accessibility@themeridian.example.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>page</wp:post_type>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
		<wp:post_name>accessibility</wp:post_name>
		<wp:menu_order>12</wp:menu_order>
	</item>

	<item>
		<title>Modern Slavery Statement</title>
		<link>https://meridian.vagra.ai/modern-slavery/</link>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Modern Slavery Statement</h2>
<p>The Meridian Hotel is committed to preventing modern slavery and human trafficking in our business and supply chains. We conduct due diligence on all suppliers, ensure fair wages and working conditions for all staff, and provide training to management on identifying and reporting concerns.</p>
<p>This statement is reviewed annually by the hotel's leadership team.</p>
<p>If you have concerns about modern slavery in connection with our operations, please contact ethics@themeridian.example.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>page</wp:post_type>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
		<wp:post_name>modern-slavery</wp:post_name>
		<wp:menu_order>13</wp:menu_order>
	</item>

